com.allisonrodenbaugh.springboothelloworld

Class Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.allisonrodenbaugh.springboothelloworld.Address

  • public class Address
extends java.lang.Object

    Class for storing address information of a customer

    The Address class is used for adding new customers to the system. Their address will be included as part of their profile.

    Note: This class does not take user input directly but simply inserts data into fields and prints out field information. This class is used for organizing customer information.

    Since:
    Fall 2018
